data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home in the heart of Jackson Township. Built in 2004, this property has been updated and meticulously cared for. Enter the home and you will be greeted by a two story foyer and stunning wood staircase. There is an oversized family room with fireplace adjacent to the foyer. The formal dining room is also located off the foyer and is perfect for those family holiday parties. A well appointed kitchen and informal eating area are open to the private backyard and outdoor entertaining area. A trex deck and stone patio with fire-pit create the perfect area for enjoying the summer evenings. The second floor boasts three generously sized bedrooms. The primary suite has a vaulted ceiling, large walk-in closet, and en suite with jacuzzi tub, separate shower, and a make-up vanity. The additional two bedrooms share a common bath. The lower level has a finished recreation/TV/exercise room and ample storage space. Enjoy the amenities Emerald Estates has to offer. There is a community swimming pool, tennis courts, basketball court, pickle ball, bocce ball, exercise room, and a clubhouse residents can use to host parties. This wonderful community also offers walking paths and sidewalks throughout the community. Please call today to schedule your private showing.
